  </head>

  <body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-light bg-light p-5">
      <div class="container-fluid">
        <h5 class="fw-bold"><i class="bi bi-arrow-clockwise" style="color: blue;"></i>Frontloops</h5>
        <form class="d-flex">
        <a class="nav-link" href="/new">Login</a>
        <a button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" href="/signup">Get Started</button></a> 
        </form>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container p-5">
      <h1 class="fw-bold text-center">Power up your frontend development skills with real-world challenges</h1>
    </div> 

    <div class="container p-5">
      <div class="d-flex justify-content-start gap-5">
        <div class="p-5  d-flex justify-content-betweens bg-warning">
          <div><h2 class="font-bold">Markup</h2>
          <span class="fs-2">$19</span> <span class="text-sm">(Lifetime access)</span>
          <p class="fs-5">Improve your HTML and CSS skills by solving 30 web interface challenges, then learn from the reference solutions and provided advice.</p>
          <a button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" href="/signup">Take this Challenge</button></a> 
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-5 d-flex justify-content-betweens bg-primary">
          <div><h2 class="font-bold">Elements</h2>
          <span class="fs-2">$19</span> <span class="text-sm">(Lifetime access)</span>
          <p class="fs-5">Improve your Javascript skills by building 30 interactive widgets from real products, then compare with provided solutions and hints.</p>
          <a button type="button" class="btn btn-warning" href="/signup">Take this Challenge</button></a> 
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="container p-5">
      <p class="fs-1 fw-bold text-center">How it Works</p>
       <div class="row">
        <div class="col" >
          <p class="text-center"><i class="bi bi-folder"  style="font-size: 4rem; color: grey;"></i></p>
          <p class="fst-italic">After you sign up and purchase a Frontloop, you will get access to all challenges with assets prepared for your kickstart.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col" >
          <p class="text-center"><i class="bi bi-laptop" style="font-size: 4rem; color: grey;"></i><p>
          <p  class="fst-italic">You code the challenge the best possible way. Don't give up and try to do it without looking at the solution.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col" >
          <p class="text-center"><i class="bi bi-lightbulb"  style="font-size: 4rem; color: grey;"></i></p>
          <p  class="fst-italic">Once you are ready, download the solution file - a working code example built by top developers including essential hints and advice.</p>
        </div>
      </div> 
    </div>

    <div class="container p-4">
     <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-6">
        <%= image_tag ("pics/boot.jpg"), width:'500px',height:'450px' %>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-6">
        <p class=" fs-2 fw-bold">These challenges will be helpful if you are:</p>
        <h5 class ="p-3"><i class="bi bi-check-circle p-2" style="color: lightgreen;"></i>A novice frontend developer who needs some practice to land a new job</h5>
        <h5 class ="p-3"><i class="bi bi-check-circle p-2" style="color: lightgreen;"></i>Already working as a developer, but feel that you are missing some parts</h5>
        <h5 class ="p-3"><i class="bi bi-check-circle p-2" style="color: lightgreen;"></i>Learning frontend theory and need more practical tasks for better learning curve</h5>
        <h5 class ="p-3"><i class="bi bi-check-circle p-2" style="color: lightgreen;"></i>Feeling intrigued about testing your frontend skills</h5>
      </div>
     </div>
    </div>
      
    <div class="container">
      <p class="fs-2 fw-bold p-5 text-center">what's included  in each course</p>
      <div class="row gap-5">
        <div class="col  text-center shadow-none p-3 mb-5 bg-light rounded"> 
            <h5>30 challenges with assets for practicing</h5>
        </div>
        <div class="col text-center  shadow-none p-3 mb-5 bg-light rounded">
             <h5>Techinical hints and advice</h5>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row gap-5">
         <div class="col text-center shadow-none p-3 mb-5 bg-light rounded">
            <h5>30 code solutions</h5>
          </div>
         <div class="col  text-center shadow-none p-3 mb-5 bg-light rounded">
             <h5>Certificate upon course completion</h5>
         </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container p-5">
      <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-6">
        <p class="fs-2 fw-bold">Get Frontloops certified</p>
        <h5 class ="p-3"><i class="bi bi-check-circle p-2" style="color: lightgreen;"></i>Complete all Frontloops challenges in your course and you'll receive a certification to share on your LinkedIn, CV or personal website.</h5>
        <h5 class ="p-3"><i class="bi bi-check-circle p-2"  style="color: lightgreen;"></i>Demonstrate experience to potential employers</h5>
        <h5 class ="p-3"><i class="bi bi-check-circle p-2" style="color: lightgreen;"></i>Boost your CV and portfolio</h5>
        <h5 class ="p-3"><i class="bi bi-check-circle p-2" style="color: lightgreen;"></i>Verifiable via <a class="text-blue" href="https://info.badgr.com/">Badgr</a></h5>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-6">
         <%= image_tag ("pics/loops.png"),width:'500px',height:'450px' %>
      </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container p-5">
      <p class="fs-2 fw-bold text-center p-2">see what others say about the course</p>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col">
           <p><i class="bi bi-person-circle p-3"  style="font-size: 3rem; color: skyblue;"></i>As a frontend developer I write a lot of complex js logic on a daily basis, however it becomes tricky when I need to implement css animations or some complicated layout positioning. That&#39;s why I loved the course - it structured my knowledge and provided best development practices.</p>
           <strong>Anton Olenin</strong>
          <p class="text-sm">Lead Frontend Developer</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col">
           <p><i class="bi bi-person-circle p-3"  style="font-size: 3rem; color: skyblue;"></i>Recently I started learning frontend technologies and this course helped me to get needed practical skills, fill my portfolio with some real code and finally land a new job as a graduate developer. That is a perfect kickstart for those who are just starting!</p>
           <strong>Anton Datsuk</strong>
           <p class="text-sm">Graduate developer</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
         <div class="col">
            <p><i class="bi bi-person-circle p-3"  style="font-size: 3rem; color: skyblue;"></i>Code examples provided after each lesson are great. They really improved my understanding of the frontend patterns and helped me in communication with developers team at work.</p>
            <strong>Paul Farrell</strong>
            <p class="text-sm">UI Designer, Team lead</p>
         </div>
        <div class="col">
            <p><i class="bi bi-person-circle p-3"  style="font-size: 3rem; color: skyblue;"></i>This course is a burst of fresh ideas for me as a professional, it really helped to see the utter ways to showcase my product still staying functional and elegant at same time.</p>
            <strong>Ester Naomi</strong>
            <p class="text-sm">Product designer</p>
         </div>
       </div>
    </div>
    
    <p class="fs-2 fw-bold text-center p-2">Sign up to Frontloops now and get a free loop from each course</p>
    <div class="d-flex justify-content-start gap-5 p-5">
    <div class="p-5  d-flex justify-content-betweens bg-warning">
       <div><h2 class="font-bold">Markup</h2>
       <span class="fs-2">$19</span> <span class="text-sm">(Lifetime access)</span>
       <p class="fs-5">Improve your HTML and CSS skills by solving 30 web interface challenges, then learn from the reference solutions and provided advice.</p>
       <a button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" href="/signup">Take this Challenge</button></a> 
    </div>
    </div>
    <div class="p-5  d-flex justify-content-betweens bg-primary">
       <div><h2 class="font-bold">Elements</h2>
       <span class="fs-2">$19</span> <span class="text-sm">(Lifetime access)</span>
       <p class="fs-5">Improve your Javascript skills by building 30 interactive widgets from real products, then compare with provided solutions and hints.</p>
      <a button type="button" class="btn btn-warning" href="/signup">Take this Challenge</button></a> 
    </div>
    </div>
    </div>
  
   <footer class="border-top border-sucess">
     <div class="row">
      <div class="col">
        <p>Part of the<a href="https://fullstackheroes.com/">Full Stack Heroes</a> ecosystem.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col">
        <p class="text-end">Follow Frontloops on <a  href="https://twitter.com/frontloopsHQ">Twitter</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
   </footer>
 </body>
